06 Jun 2017 00:27






Yeah for a couple of those entries I was going for more of a general combination of factors that lead to one outcome or another - there isn't a single allele that causes myopia either as far as I know, but there are a combination of genetic factors that can cause it and thus make it hereditary.

And yeah, you're right about some of phrasing. In cases like this I actually try and avoid being that technical, because in my headcanon these SCP articles can be read by a whole range of Foundation personnel and they won't all share the same educational backgrounds. But, there's also the issue that I'm not a geneticist and figured it was safer to go with the  version than something that was specific and totally wrong.

I'll add a bit more to the description of the images, that's a good idea.







